pullRequest.title: KOGITO-2433 - BPMN Editor in VSCODE can not open file with missing SimulationAttributeSets
pullRequest.bodyText:
Hi @romartin, @LuboTerifaj, @domhanak,
another small fix for third party editors better support. I provided fix for both Business Central and Kogito, since fix looks easy and safe for me. I provided tests for both Business Central and Kogito as well? Also I tested VS Code extension and Business Central and both loading provided file without any issues, so I think this PR is ready for review. Thank you!


VSIX can be downloaded here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ab4dlZued6NFlgWlz0OR9WPd2FAbNKRz/view?usp=sharing
Business Central can be downloaded here:  https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tdHWSgJzw09ciYvUyM_B2coUrp69-q1_/view?usp=sharing
